omepage":"","overview":"Dopo la misteriosa scomparsa della propria bambina, una giovane coppia inizia a ricevere strani video e si rende conto che qualcuno ha filmato la loro vita quotidiana, persino i momenti più intimi. La polizia mette la casa sotto sorveglianza per tentare di sorprendere il voyeur, ma la famiglia inizia a sgretolarsi a mano a mano che i segreti si svelano sotto lo sguardo attento di occhi che li osservano da ogni parte."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"누군가 지켜보고 있다","runtime":127,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"어린 딸이 불가사의하게 실종된 후, 젊은 부부는 이상한 동영상을 받고 누군가 그들의 일상을, 심지어 가장 사적인 순간까지 촬영해 왔다는 것을 깨닫는다. 경찰은 훔쳐보는 사람을 잡으려 집 주변을 감시하지만, 사방에서 지켜보는 감시의 시선 속에서 가족의 비밀이 드러나며 가족은 무너지기 시작한다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"默视录","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在一个监控处处的城市，一个快退休的警探，负责调查一个从事诈骗的年轻人。在监视与反监视的过程中，两个人都被迫得穷途末路。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Mo Shi Lu","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Po tajemniczym zniknięciu córeczki młode małżeństwo zaczyna otrzymywać dziwne filmy i zdaje sobie sprawę, że ktoś sfilmował ich codzienne życie, nawet najbardziej intymne chwile. Policja objęła dom obserwacją, próbując zaskoczyć podglądacza, ale rodzina zaczyna się rozpadać, gdy pod czujnym okiem oczu obserwujących ją ze wszystkich stron na jaw wychodzą tajemnice."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":126,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Na de mysterieuze verdwijning van hun dochtertje ontvangt een jong stel vreemde video's en realiseert zich dat iemand hun dagelijks leven heeft gefilmd - zelfs op hun meest intieme momenten. De politie zet toezicht rond hun huis om de voyeur te vangen, maar het gezin begint af te brokkelen terwijl geheimen zich ontrafelen onder het toezicht van ogen die hen van alle kanten in de gaten houden."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"女兒在公園遊樂場離奇失蹤後，一對年輕夫妻與母親的生活也徹底變了樣。他們絕望奔找女兒，直到私密偷拍光碟送達，案情出現一線曙光，卻發現有人正在監視著這個家。一家人不得不在門口裝上監控反制窺探者，卻讓自己的生活暴露得更加蒼白赤裸。隨著偷拍者的身分逐漸曝光，每個家庭成員終將迎來屬於自己的真相⋯⋯。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Stranger Eyes","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"La petite fille de Darren a disparu. Lorsque des images mystérieuses apparaissent, Darren soupçonne son voisin Goh, d'être le voyeur lié à la disparition de sa fille. De plus en plus inquiet, Darren décide de traquer Goh..."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Vigilados","runtime":126,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"La hija de dos años de una joven pareja de Singapur desaparece sin dejar rastro. Tres meses más tarde, cuando empiezan a perder la esperanza de encontrarla, reciben una serie de vídeos que prueban que alguien ha estado grabando imágenes de sus vidas cotidianas."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Stranger Eyes","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un bărbat își caută obsesiv fiica dispărută după ce a primit videoclipuri tulburătoare care îi expun secretele, ceea ce duce la o confruntare înfricoșătoare cu voyeurul."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Vigilats","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Després de la misteriosa desaparició del seu nadó, una jove parella comença a rebre vídeos estranys i s'adona que algú ha estat filmant la seva vida diària, fins i tot els seus moments més íntims. La policia munta una vigilància al voltant de casa seva per atrapar el voyeur, però la família es comença a desfer a mesura que es revelen secrets sota l'escrutini d'uns ulls que els observen des de tot arreu."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1200674,"adult":false,"title":"A Dark Story","video":false,"overview":"Vito and Carla have been separated for a long time, they have three children and used to love each other deeply before their love went sour. Now Vito has a new life and Carla has a partner. At a time when everyone feels tragedy can be avoided, fate is on their other side. One night, Vito disappeared. From that day on, no one ever heard from him again. His disappearance triggered an investigation involving all those involved. But is there really an irrefutable truth in these cases?","genre_ids":[53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.396,"vote_count":46,"poster_path":"/qEMkV2Un6wy34y3UtRnzfE7yBOh.jpg","release_date":"2024-05-16","vote_average":6.522,"backdrop_path":"/gKWLUJotQ1U1ovo6E2LjDO4HRt2.jpg","original_title":"Una storia nera","original_language":"it"},{"id":1183761,"adult":false,"title":"Here Now","video":false,"overview":"Sophie is a twenty-year-old American who has lived her life in isolation, cut off from the world. While on vacation in Palermo with her sister, she meets Giulio and his group of Sicilian friends during her final 24 hours before returning to California. Eager to break free from her sheltered past, Sophie embarks on a whirlwind romance with Giulio.","genre_ids":[53,80,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9366,"vote_count":79,"poster_path":"/gVL8eoeI5BgWbFi7E1GGlbrEg5y.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-31","vote_average":5.532,"backdrop_path":"/73TvqmSy3VeVzxfCJqUFxymuV0I.jpg","original_title":"Fino alla fine","original_language":"it"},{"id":1209450,"adult":false,"title":"National Family","video":false,"overview":"Don Poli, the patriarch of a family embedded in politics, faces the change of party in his state - after a hundred years in power - losing all his privileges. Humiliated and angry, he threatens to disinherit his family and leave to rebuild his life. This forces his children (Kippy, Ramses and Belén) to take extreme measures to ensure their future, causing everything that could go wrong to turn out worse.","genre_ids":[35,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3429,"vote_count":90,"poster_path":"/oSAzrJ0AjFZLUCcHT8YAnuD7egp.jpg","release_date":"2023-12-28","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/2qaFnZxMkj5nKz1MWinaVNfg7T7.jpg","original_title":"Familia Nacional","original_language":"es"},{"id":661120,"adult":false,"title":"Palkó Csinom","video":false,"overview":"The musical adventure film goes back to the early eighteenth century, the times of the battles between the Hungarian insurrectionists and the pro-Austrians. Palkó and Jankó are about to join the insurrectionist army when they clash with a pro-Austrian troop. Jankó is captured and put in Count Koháry's prison.","genre_ids":[12,36,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6094,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/ywEUaP5ovp069HDOD6CO2Qd9x4p.jpg","release_date":"1973-01-01","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Csínom Palkó","original_language":"en"},{"id":1491379,"adult":false,"title":"Stripped Down: The Making of ‘Anora’","video":false,"overview":"Making of documentary surrounding the production of ‘Anora’","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2527,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/iX9eX8dcKO2JWxtjFhXdAH3zYp9.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-29","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/kCE2rdWp18EDd6ZnPFCVUmUl1sZ.jpg","original_title":"Stripped Down: The Making of ‘Anora’","original_language":"en"},{"id":71362,"adult":false,"title":"Hello, Moscow!","video":false,"overview":"At the amateur talent show the boy, accompanying himself on the accordion, sings a song about Moscow... The plot of the movie is based on the story of the director of the school about how this accordion, once belonging to a cadre worker who died during a demonstration in 1905, has been in many hands before it got to the guys.","genre_ids":[10402,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3929,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/tA10PvTgWGtVp2fZxyQOYs6ouCT.jpg","release_date":"1945-06-06","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Здравствуй, Москва!","original_language":"ru"},{"id":965571,"adult":false,"title":"Patriots Time","video":false,"overview":"The brothers Sultan and Bekzat Ibrayev are serving faithfully in the Armed Forces of Kazakhstan, and at the same time they are in family disagreement. Sultan is a valiant intelligence officer and Bekzat is a talented fighter pilot. While an international terrorist organization prepares a carefully planned attack on the country's strategically important facilities, the brothers have to face not only a mortal threat, but also face a family confrontation related to their dead father. Circumstances force them to unite in order to save human lives, and the brothers eventually understand that their homeland and family are the most valuable thing they have.","genre_ids":[28,10752,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5672,"vote_count":133,"poster_path":"/A4QM6oF4UNNhQh1f9pRdXvyKW5s.jpg","release_date":"2022-04-28","vote_average":7.485,"backdrop_path":"/xCt3Ha6hhHep5pwiW2FSenC59Gn.jpg","original_title":"Время патриотов","original_language":"ru"},{"id":210763,"adult":false,"title":"A","video":false,"overview":"A film director fades away from the industry after the failed love with the heroine of his movie. After being rehabilitated, he learns that some people conspired his fall and decides to take revenge.","genre_ids":[10749,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3768,"vote_count":110,"poster_path":"/y3DH68oWOGMZ637tqYHfTGU4Bif.jpg","release_date":"1998-02-12","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/2LWK3EYLVsY0tYBWS5KjwNBymWR.jpg","original_title":"ಎ","original_language":"kn"},{"id":541668,"adult":false,"title":"Mad","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4394,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/ezUD9aVxBR8vEIp2Qi41Jz4hUNd.jpg","release_date":"2017-06-29","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Mad","original_language":"fr"},{"id":643397,"adult":false,"title":"Girl on the Moon","video":false,"overview":"Someone from another planet crashed on Earth and evil is chasing him, and then love appears, and it defeats evil through an amulet.","genre_ids":[10749,878,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1397,"vote_count":30,"poster_path":"/6NjAgV83YtHeCbOT0DibWLUOiWF.jpg","release_date":"2012-04-12","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Ый кыыhа","original_language":"ru"},{"id":460179,"adult":false,"title":"Classmates","video":false,"overview":"Two students at college were friends until a girl appeared and by the workings of fate was beloved by both. The girl has given her heart to one of the classmates, unknown to the other.  The youth confesses his love, and is plunged into despair when told that her heart is another's. Coldly the classmates part, when the next day they start on their divergent paths of life. Years later, they meet again and while the trio enjoy a pleasant chat, a message calls the husband away, leaving his wife to entertain. The chum takes advantage of his absence to renew his protestations of love, which are spurned by the wife, who attempts to avoid him. He follows, whereupon the wife sends him reeling down the stairs, just as the husband reenters. The woman's denunciation of the friend brings about a terrific combat.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1217,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1908-02-01","vote_average":3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Classmates","original_language":"en"},{"id":1067309,"adult":false,"title":"Black and Bitter","video":false,"overview":"Jennifer's husband determines for her to get a pregnant, however, she wants to leave with the man she loves.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0505,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/tW5QiwebLYeauYyYqpVgu1UplUo.jpg","release_date":"2021-04-30","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Black and Bitter","original_language":"en"},{"id":195814,"adult":false,"title":"The Beniker Gang","video":false,"overview":"When his younger friends go up for adoption, threatening their extended family, an orphaned teen helps them discourage potential parents.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4246,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/4l45Mtbn9M62wCs5wLgrq2vETAt.jpg","release_date":"1984-11-02","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/aMz6aVlHxP3qko7T3ie4aBjmq14.jpg","original_title":"The Beniker Gang","original_language":"en"},{"id":192186,"adult":false,"title":"Zombie 90: Extreme Pestilence","video":false,"overview":"Two doctors are trying to stop a rampant epidemic of zombieism. They fend off zombies spilling many a gallon of blood in the process.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1068,"vote_count":25,"poster_path":"/pleREieQYbtILB0t1uRnjyYoild.jpg","release_date":"1991-06-02","vote_average":3.1,"backdrop_path":"/6yjAWXDl5FsK7tnKtrWMiqGgiNU.jpg","original_title":"Zombie 90: Extreme Pestilence","original_language":"en"},{"id":64838,"adult":false,"title":"Made in Paris","video":false,"overview":"Diane lives with publisher Hermann but everything is spoiled when Worms, Hermann’s loyal author and friend, reveals in his new book the affair he once had with Diane, in a highly subjective manner. She soon discovers the contents of the work, which Hermann tries to hide from her, and takes on a lawyer to defend her privacy. But this is only the beginning of a mess that simply gets worse and worse, leading to an unexpected, brutal ending.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1508,"vote_count":12,"poster_path":"/hvarq69Cw4BxXvL7WeGYNcbWQ7P.jpg","release_date":"2006-11-29","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/8NkgECZVK5MWPLXnR2nZnEX7iar.jpg","original_title":"Je pense à vous","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1181511,"adult":false,"title":"The Benetón Family","video":false,"overview":"Toni, a grumpy in his fifties, avoids children at all costs. His life changes when he suddenly has to take care of his sister's five adopted children, each from a different country. Toni will have to deal with new parenthood and cultural differences.","genre_ids":[35,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4291,"vote_count":60,"poster_path":"/5VISxbDN4YSFZao3MAkElC4WE6O.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-22","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/oobxTUUtUZSqnLJyHIZwfBrMIMe.jpg","original_title":"La familia Benetón","original_language":"es"},{"id":382139,"adult":false,"title":"Mongolian Princess","video":false,"overview":"One day, you fell from the sky.  I never knew loving somebody could bring so much happiness.  I see the world differently because of you.  I am a different person because you live in my heart.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2224,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/xWh6Z8VOJTxHrglvsWHqOHLCmJ4.jpg","release_date":"2015-03-19","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/sIO6Gzo1zRfnxuZsWgG6Gqvg0xX.jpg","original_title":"몽골리안 프린세스","original_language":"ko"},{"id":860393,"adult":false,"title":"One Night Stand","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2125,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/VuPNG1jrgkFX0c6tlTOhFL7Wqo.jpg","release_date":"2017-03-28","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"원나잇스탠드","original_language":"ko"},{"id":221476,"adult":false,"title":"Halalabad Blues","video":false,"overview":"A warm-hearted and biting romance about the impossible love between a Danish woman and a Turkish man","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7184,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/AqfkNGxDPyHyb5ZqkN26b1Mhvgb.jpg","release_date":"2002-11-29","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/5KOS3iwVb0BLpJv3wqxwtTnlP47.jpg","original_title":"Halalabad Blues","original_language":"da"},{"id":152848